data.description: Welcome Home to Viera East Golf Course on the 15th. Fairway! This Beautiful Home Features 3 Bedroom/2 Bath, Tile Floors in the Main Areas, High Ceilings, Carpeted Guest Bedrooms, Master Bedroom Boasts; Slider to the Screened Patio/Laminate Flooring/Large Shower/2 Closets (1 Walk-In), Guest Bath has a Tub, Laundry Room, Gas Range for the Chef in you, Nice Appliances, Breakfast Bar, Dining Area, Sky Light, Ceiling Fans in all Bedrooms & Living Room, Roll Down Hurricane Shutters Throughout, Fresh Exterior Paint 2023, A/C System 11/2019, New Roof 2019, Gas Water Heater 2022, HOA Responsible for Everything Outside: Exterior Paint, Lawn, Mulch, Tree & Bush Trimming for a Whether your Starting Out or Retired this is Maintenance Free Life! Come see for yourself, you will not be disappointed! Amenities GALORE!! Visit Viera East Golf Course Residents Club it Boasts: 2 Meeting Rooms, Full Kitchen, Library, Exercise Room w/Work-Out Equipment for Ever Part of Your Body & a Heated Pool w/Hot Tub To soothe those achy muscles!  Bocce Ball, Tennis & Pickel Ball Courts, you have it all!!!!!!
